<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">throat</ENAMEX>, is eaten by an <ENAMEX TYPE="ANIMAL">alligator</ENAMEX>, and then what is left of his <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">body</ENAMEX> is consumed
