Buffy , vampires are much easier to dispatch: A simple wooden stake will
do it after all--or, in an emergency, a broken guitar neck. In <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">the 1992</TIMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Francis</ENAMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Ford Coppola</ENAMEX> version of <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Bram Stoker</ENAMEX>'s <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Dracula</ENAMEX> , <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Dracula</ENAMEX> dies when he is
