<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Anthony Hopkins</ENAMEX>, playing the film's mad vampire <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">hunter</ENAMEX>, seems to put more store
in chopping off <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">heads</ENAMEX> than impaling hearts. In <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">John Carpenter</ENAMEX>'s
