<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">ironing</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">board</ENAMEX>. When <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Lugosi</ENAMEX> takes to the air it's in the form of a giant <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Asian</ENAMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">fruit</ENAMEX> bat. (He also turns into a hyena and an armadillo, <ENAMEX TYPE="ANIMAL">species</ENAMEX> that are
similarly not native to <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Transylvania</ENAMEX>.)

