well established. <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Cruise</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">gathers</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Brad Pitt</ENAMEX> into one of many <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">homoerotic</ENAMEX> embraces
