<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">unnatural</ENAMEX> to begin with, maybe that's OK.

            
               Proposed <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Standard</ENAMEX> : retractable
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">fangs</ENAMEX> as default characteristic. Strongly recommend, when appropriate,
